2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The proposed approach involves end-to-end training of deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a novel approach for person re-identification using deep neural networks, which can be considered as an application of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The datasets used in the experiments are related to multimedia, as they contain images and videos of people. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): Person re-identification has applications in security and surveillance, which can be related to the field of cryptography and security.
